attributes.description: Agentcore gateway dashboard showcasing invocation performance and operational health.

params.markdown:
# Gateway

This dashboard provides insights into the following:
- Gateway invocation metrics, including total requests, Lambda calls, and MCP (Model Context Protocol) invocations across different protocols
- Method-specific performance tracking with invocation counts, latency, duration, and error rates broken down by tool calls vs non-tool calls
- Error analysis and monitoring, separating system errors, user errors, and total errors with detailed breakdowns by resource and target
- Performance optimisation insights, including throttling detection, target execution time, and latency vs duration comparisons across gateway methods

filter.query: aws.dimensions.Operation : "InvokeGateway"  and ( NOT aws.dimensions.Name : * ) and ( NOT aws.dimensions.Method : * ) and (NOT aws.dimensions.Resource : * ) and aws.dimensions.Protocol : *

embeddableConfig.description: Requests made to each Data Plane API. Each API call counts as one invocation regardless of the response status.
embeddableConfig.title: Gateway invocations
